<div id='panel'>
<h1>A Stone in time</h1>
<h2>
[ <a href='edit.pl?id=a-stone-in-time-gallery-1'>
Edit</a> ]
</h2>

<div style='text-align:left;' id='key'>

<span class='tab'>Characters</span>

<div> </div>
<div style='margin:1px 0px 1px 0px;'>
<p align='center'>

<table cellspacing='10' cellpadding='0' width='550'>
<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-apacalypes.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-apacalypes.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

Apocalypses is the leader of the Dark Whale Empire. In his timeline he will destroy the machine hives created by parasite intruders and exterminate dolphin kind for creating the invaders and letting them get out of hand. Apocalypses is the fusion of Arkonviox and a young Orca named Clondike.

<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-arknovious.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-arknovious.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

Arknovious is the Arkon of Strata an element with no weaknesses. He is a vile creature with a vast amount of power who wants nothing more then destruction and chaos. Arknovious unlike the other Arkon's is a beast and cannot communicate or reason. Arknovious wears the Dolphin armor "the Wings of Chaos".

<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-arkonviox.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-arkonviox.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

Arkonviox is the Arkon of lightening and bearer of the Dolphin armor "The Wings of Burden". Unable to forgive himself for the death of his love Nautika, Arkonviox transforms guilt and sadness into rage and aggression. 

<p>His curse is to live forever with a piece of Nautika that remained, an egg known as the Enigma. If the Enigma ever hatched it could create and destroy life.</p>

<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-conquest-arkonviox.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-conquest-arkonviox.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

The Arkon of Ice and the Stone in Time who created all existence. He bears the Dolphin Armor "The Wings of Judgment". In an alternate reality his universe was on the brink of collapse. His very existence would cause a time crash that would wipe out all life. With no other choice he would create a time portal to a place and time where all are one: the eternal dream.

<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-crestoe.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-crestoe.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

A Dolphin whose race the Thirian's get wiped out by the Seven Dark Whales. Becoming the last of his race Crestoe swears to avenge his kind by destroying the Seven Dark Whales and to travel back in time and prevent their clan from ever existing.

<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-cyberdolphin.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-cyberdolphin.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

When the Arkon of Ice and a strange anomaly called Vernineus merge they create an army of assimilated dolphins in a conquest for control of the world. 


<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-darkwhale.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-darkwhale.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

The Seven Dark Whales were sent into the past by Apocalypses whose existence is from intervention with the time line. A young orca named Clondike and Arkonviox must be captured and taken to a future world where desperation forces them to merge giving birth to Apocalypse. Apocalypes will save the world from a dangerous threat but will create a new nightmare, a world ruled by Orca kind.

<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-dazer.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-dazer.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

In the ancient land of Mu lived a benevolent race of beings known as the seraphim's. They bestowed great power on those who would integrate into their society. Those of Mu were known as the Magians. Dazer is a Magian Blue Whale with the elemental powers of Ice, Lightening and Fire.

<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-earthclan-crestoe.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-earthclan-crestoe.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

Crestoe, overwhelmed by the Seven Dark Whales sacrifices himself to save his friends. But when the evil Magian Sitna returns to our world creating a time ripple Crestoe is given another chance. Awakening from his death, Crestoe vanishes into a world ruled by Sitna's Earth Clan. Crestoe joins Earth Clan and from it gains a vast amount of strength and power.

<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-monark.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-monark.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

Monark is the Arkon of Fire and bearer of the Dolphin Armor "The Wings of War". When the Arkons were divided and sent to different time lines Monark ended up in the far past. Because of his vast power, arrogance and pride dolphin kind came to refer to him as the Dolphin God of War.

<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-nautika.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-nautika.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

Nautika is the Arkon of water and bearer of the Dolphin Armor "The Wings of Vengence". Arkonviox was responsible for her death and the stealing of her child the Enigma. In the far future the Lumirian's use their technology to create a clone of Nautika and send her back in time with a mission. But her former life does not allow her to forget who was responsible for her death.


<tr>
<td align='left' valign='bottom'>

<a href='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-vernineus.png' target='_blank'>
<img src='../eccoserv/asit/spritex48-vernineus.png' border='0' style='float:left;margin-right:10px;' /></a>

The Stone in Time learns that the world will be eventually be destroyed in a time crash unless he intervenes. He creates a Dolphin and sends him into the past to prevent the events that will result in the crash. But for every action is a reaction, a sinister side is created and follows the Dolphin hero back. Its purpose is to destroy the lone hero and merge with him creating a backfire on the eternal dreamers plan.

</table>
</p>
</div>
